{"tid":1421644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大 WIFI 今天凌晨未能登入連登　被疑刻意封鎖　學生轟「同中國有咩分別」","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:35:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96ecba4b51621b6796e847813ca88885a8127f54","tid":1421644,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hkulihkg-05_nPmi4_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhkulihkg-05_nPmi4_1200x0.png&h=643ec02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有香港大學學生對《立場新聞》表示，今日凌晨無法通過港大校內的「HKU」及「eduroam」WIFI 登入 LIHKG討論區（簡稱：連登），畫面分別顯示「The URL you requested has been blocked」及「Your connection is not private」，登入其他網站、包括成人網站，則未受影響，有學生質疑校方是因近日反修例運動而採取的行動，封鎖連登。<br />\n<br />\n大約於今晨 1 時半，有港大學生以需要個人密碼的「HKU」及「eduroam」校內 WIFI 嘗試連結連登討論區，惟兩者均無法連上網站，只有使用由政府管理的「<a href=\"http://Wi-Fi.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWi-Fi.HK&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=01fc7807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Wi-Fi.HK</a> via HKU」WIFI 或個人網絡熱點才能順利連上連登討論區。<br />\n<br />\n有住港大舍堂的學生表示，舍堂內全層的同學均未能使用「HKU」WIFI 連結連登討論區，惟連結 Facebook 甚至成人網站則暢通無阻，亦有學生需要連 VPN 才能登入連登討論區。不少學生在網上發表意見指校方封鎖網站的行為是「封鎖言論自由」、「終於喺香港上連登都要翻牆」，斥責港大的行為「同中國有咩分別」。<br />\n<br />\n現時，港大「HKU」及「eduroam」WIFI 已能重新連結連登網站。《立場新聞》就事件詢問校方的回應，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/港大-wifi-今天凌晨未能登入連登-被疑刻意封鎖-學生轟-同中國有咩分別/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-wifi-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A5%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E7%96%91%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%BD%9F-%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5%2F&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=9d3a0bc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-wifi-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A5%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E7%96%91%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%BD%9F-%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5%2F&h=b2f15c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/港大-wifi-今天凌晨未能登入連登-被疑刻意封鎖-學生轟-同中國有咩分別/</a>"},{"pid":"8c66ea85e2d3b8914aac9d4eda9afd92d3b42c10","tid":1421644,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地愛黨愛國 點解禁我地"},{"pid":"841c5c902d42303648f6608535c9b69297abf066","tid":1421644,"uid":202730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eee24c7dee39e5e101180fb378fbb397998a2e","tid":1421644,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf9a23ef3268c582554b30fc793e81f143ed428","tid":1421644,"uid":210740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"有住港大舍堂的學生表示，舍堂內全層的同學均未能使用「HKU」WIFI 連結連登討論區，惟連結 Facebook <span style=\"color: red;\">甚至成人網站</span>則暢通無阻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d5ffcf2286bca60e3f4da1fc6b6fb68637f815","tid":1421644,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"黨校。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb243c50353ba727a810294e0f82e45ca6b4eed","tid":1421644,"uid":193026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:52:15.000Z","msg":"小心呀，可能有IT狗，搞HKU WIFI，<a href=\"http://搞到lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%90%9E%E5%88%B0lihkg.com&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=7fab4246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">搞到lihkg.com</a>係連去釣魚網站先<br />\n<br />\n睇下張cert有無古怪先好用來login<br />\n<br />\n多數browser，網址旁邊都會有個鎖仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9Jmzxv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9Jmzxv.png&h=89230078&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁落去個鎖仔，view certificate/查看證書之類啦，唔知正體中文點譯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WU8YZe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WU8YZe.png&h=1a654206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇睇張cert係咪咁樣，唔係既話唔好上<br />\n同埋即刻話俾全世界知，HKU班垃圾搞網絡攻擊，MITH佢地既學生，想偷唔知咩料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8yYUUwM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8yYUUwM.png&h=5c91b5ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0892546b9a84f096088e2f18a7e318a9a5f4088","tid":1421644,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"原來有人貼左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}